Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: markdown_image_replacer
Version: 0.0.2
Summary: Markdown images' URL replacing with copying/downloading images to specific directory
Project-URL: Homepage, https://github.com/panzhongxian/markdown_image_replacer
Project-URL: Bug Tracker, https://github.com/panzhongxian/markdown_image_replacer/issues
Author-email: panzhongxian <panzhongxian0532@gmail.com>
License-File: LICENSE
Classifier: License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License
Classifier: Operating System :: OS Independent
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 3
Requires-Python: >=3.7
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown



```bash
python -m markdown_image_replacer \
   $HOME/blog/content/posts/my-first-post.md \
   --src_img_root $HOME/blog/static \
   --dst_md_file $HOME/blog/content/posts/my-first-post2.md \
   --dst_img_root $HOME/blog/static \
   --dst_img_rel_dir images/my-first-post
```



